#Rete Based Authoring Shell

Author a Knowledge Base, with associated rules, in a simple shell like environment.

## Knowledge base

what does the ability to describe institutions and activities afford?
what needs to be described in an institution or activity?

## Rules

What are the semantics of rules?
What are the components of rules?


## Action Description and evaluation

Tracery like grammar expansion

## Simulation

How do the rules and knowledge base combine to enable a simulation


